Warren Finnerty https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Warren_Finnerty 0 Warren Finnerty (April 9, 1925 – December 22, 1974) was an American actor best known for his Obie award-winning performance as the character "Leach" in the stage production The Connection (1959).
